---
// src/components/WhyUs.astro
---
<div class="text-left space-y-6">
  <div class="text-center mb-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#2F4340] tracking-tight">
      Why Choose Us?
    </h2>
    <div class="w-60 h-1 bg-[#D9744B] mx-auto mt-2 rounded-full"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg text-slate-800 font-medium leading-relaxed">
    <p>
      At <strong>Quality Landscape and Leisure</strong>, we believe your property's outdoor space should be just as functional and beautiful as your home's interior. Our professional crew is dedicated to delivering dependable local service, elite craftsmanship, and meticulous attention to detail on every single project—ranging from weekly lawn maintenance and detailed planting designs to premium brick patios and custom hardscapes.
    </p>
    <p>
      We take immense pride in installing custom outdoor living spaces that not only stand out in the neighborhood, but also provide families across the Wabash Valley area with a functional, inviting place to relax, entertain, and enjoy for years to come.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Dynamic Call to Actions -->
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 justify-center items-center">
    <a 
      href="/contact" 
      class="w-full sm:w-auto bg-[#2F4340] text-white 
        font-bold px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl shadow-md 
        hover:bg-[#D9744B] hover:border-slate-200 hover:border
        transition-colors duration-200 text-base"
    >
      Contact Us For Quality
    </a>
  </div>
</div>